(17, 4, 1, '', '2019-08-13 23:47:43', 879, 4699, '387c83c0fdf38413457562b7f795856e2f83e7fd', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":\"82\",\"title\":\"Hot\\u00e9is de Bal Harbour oferecem privil\\u00e9gios exclusivos\",\"alias\":\"hoteis-de-bal-harbour-oferecem-privilegios-exclusivos\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Bal Harbour \\u00e9 hoje um dos destinos mais badalados de Miami e engloba o famoso Shopping ao ar livre, Bal Harbour Shops, com 100 das mais famosas grifes do mundo; o exclusivo cinco estrelas, de frente para o mar The Ritz-Carlton Bal Harbour, o hist\\u00f3rico e tradicional Sea View Hotel, o novo boutique hotel Bal Harbour Quarzo Hotel e o St. Regis Bal Harbour Resort. A cidade tamb\\u00e9m promove sess\\u00f5es de cinema ao ar livre e exposi\\u00e7\\u00f5es de arte p\\u00fablica pelas ruas da cidade. O destino oferece um programa gratuito que facilita a entrada de h\\u00f3spedes de Bal Harbour aos melhores museus de Miami.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Munidos de um cart\\u00e3o pessoal, eles t\\u00eam acesso gratuito a alguns dos mais aclamados museus e galerias privativas da regi\\u00e3o, como o Wolfsonian Museum; o Perez Art Museum (PAMM); o Museum of Contemporary Art (MOCA), a Rubell Family Collection; e a De La Cruz Collection.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\/hoteis_bal_harbour_st_regis.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"St. Regis\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" title=\\\"St. Regis\\\" caption=\\\"false\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"1024\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Os privil\\u00e9gios especiais s\\u00e3o v\\u00e1lidos para quem ficar hospedado em um dos 4 hot\\u00e9is de Bal Harbour \\u2013 St. Regis Bal Harbour, Ritz-Carlton Bal Harbour, Quarzo Bal Harbour e Sea View Hotel. A Flot Viagens montou um roteiro exclusivo com estes hot\\u00e9is, confira.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Confira a lista completa de museus que participam da a\\u00e7\\u00e3o:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Museum of Contemporary Art (MoCA)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>P\\u00e9rez Art Museum Miami (PAMM)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Phillip and Patricia Frost Museum of Science<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Fairchild Tropical Botanic Garden<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The Bass Museum of Art<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Wolfsonian \\u2013 FIU<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Patricia and Phillip frost Art Museum<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Rubell Family Collection (RFC)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The Margulies Collection at The Warehouse<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The de la Cruz Collection<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Institute of Contemporary Art (ICA)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>MDC Museum of Art and Design<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>National YoungArts Foundation<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>NSU Art Museum Fort Lauderdale<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>HistoryMiami Museum<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Jewish Museum of Florida \\u2013 FIU<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Lowe Art Museum \\u2013 University of Miami<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\/hoteis_bal_harbour_art_museum.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"P\\u00e9rez Art Museum Miami (PAMM)\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\/hoteis_bal_harbour_museum_contemporany.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Museum of Contemporary Art (MoCA)\\\" title=\\\"Museum of Contemporary Art (MoCA)\\\" caption=\\\"false\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"495\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"10\",\"created\":\"2019-06-21 23:51:55\",\"created_by\":\"879\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-13 23:47:43\",\"modified_by\":\"879\",\"checked_out\":\"879\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-08-13 23:47:33\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-06-21 23:51:55\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog\\\\\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\\\\\/hoteis_bal_harbour.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"left\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":5,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0);
