(26, 1, 1, '', '2019-08-16 19:54:28', 879, 11593, '7c43bf2a4bfa75cf7c8035f6a95ce7e303944477', '{\"id\":1,\"asset_id\":\"61\",\"title\":\"Su\\u00ed\\u00e7a e seus trens panor\\u00e2micos Premium\",\"alias\":\"suica-e-seus-trens-panoramicos-premium\",\"introtext\":\"<p>As rotas ferrovi\\u00e1rias panor\\u00e2micas da Su\\u00ed\\u00e7a (como o Glacier Express e o Bernina Express) est\\u00e3o entre as mais belas rotas ferrovi\\u00e1rias do mundo e fazem parte do patrim\\u00f4nio e da hist\\u00f3ria do pa\\u00eds. Elas passam pelo mais majestoso cen\\u00e1rio montanhoso, vales e aldeias id\\u00edlicas; ao longo de lagos cristalinos e glaciares.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Seus passageiros privilegiados desfrutam de esplendores c\\u00eanicos impressionantes e conforto de viagem superior. <br \\/>Os trens panor\\u00e2micos da Su\\u00ed\\u00e7a abrangem uma feliz harmonia entre a alta tecnologia e a natureza celestial. \\u00c9 uma combina\\u00e7\\u00e3o cativante que nunca deixa de fascinar.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Bernina Express<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Este trem panor\\u00e2mico conecta o norte ao sul da Europa \\u2013 diretamente na Rhaetian Railway, Patrim\\u00f4nio Mundial da UNESCO, passando por geleiras em seu caminho at\\u00e9 as palmeiras. Cruzar os Alpes a bordo do Bernina Express \\u00e9, certamente, uma das maneiras mais espetaculares de conhecer a regi\\u00e3o. Ao longo do caminho, o Bernina Express segue em estilo hollywoodiano pelo Viaduto Landwasser, a famosa estrutura de 65 metros de altura da Rhaetian Railway, tombada Patrim\\u00f4nio Mundial da UNESCO. No total, o trem passa por 55 t\\u00faneis e mais de 195 pontes no percurso de Chur a Tirano. Os viajantes s\\u00e3o presenteados com cen\\u00e1rios fascinantes durante a viagem, como a curva de Montebello, com vista para o maci\\u00e7o de Bernina; a geleira Morteratsch; os tr\\u00eas lagos Lej Pitschen, Lej Nair e Lago Bianco, o Alp Gr\\u00fcm, e o viaduto circular de Brusio. No ver\\u00e3o, a viagem pode ser estendida de Tirano a Lugano, a bordo do \\u00f4nibus Bernina Express.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Novidade: A partir de maio de 2019, o Bernina Express tamb\\u00e9m vai ligar Landquart a Tirano.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/suica_trem\\/suica_trem2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"543\\\" height=\\\"362\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">Fatos Bernina Express (trem)<\\/span><\\/strong><br \\/>Rota: St. Moritz \\/ Chur \\u2013 Tirano (It\\u00e1lia) ou vice-versa<br \\/>Dist\\u00e2ncia: 156 km<br \\/>Dura\\u00e7\\u00e3o: 4 h 13 min<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">Dicas de excurs\\u00e3o:<\\/span><\\/strong><br \\/>Estrada de ferro Arosa \\u2013 de Chur a Arosa em uma hora. Em apenas 26 km, o trem sobe a incr\\u00edveis 1000 metros de altitude <br \\/>Museu Ferrovi\\u00e1rio de Albula \\u2013 mais de 600 exposi\\u00e7\\u00f5es sobre os mais de 100 anos de hist\\u00f3ria ferrovi\\u00e1ria, como uma das \\u00faltimas locomotivas \\u201cCrocodilo\\u201d<br \\/>Gandria \\u2013 um pitoresco vilarejo aos p\\u00e9s do Monte Br\\u00e9<br \\/>Monte San Salvatore \\u2013 um dos cen\\u00e1rios mais belos ao longo do Lago Lugano<br \\/>Palm Express \\u2013 rica em contrastes, conecta Lugano a St. Moritz em cerca de quatro horas de viagem de \\u00f4nibus<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Comida &amp; Bebida<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>O minibar do Bernina Express oferece deliciosos petiscos e bebidas refrescantes<br \\/>O trem n\\u00e3o possui vag\\u00e3o-restaurante. Na hora do almo\\u00e7o, o trem para na cidade italiana de Tirano<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/suica_trem\\/suica_trem3.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"489\\\" height=\\\"326\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Glacier Express<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>A viagem, famosa por ser feita no trem expresso mais lento do mundo, conduz os viajantes pelos Alpes em cerca de oito horas, passando por 91 t\\u00faneis e mais de 290 pontes. O Glacier Express oferece uma viagem aos sentidos \\u2013 da Engadine ao Matterhorn. Em sua jornada relaxante a partir do deslumbrante St. Moritz ao igualmente sofisticado Zermatt, o Glacier Express delicia os viajantes com atra\\u00e7\\u00f5es c\\u00eanicas e tecnologias ultramodernas. Com suas enormes janelas panor\\u00e2micas, o Glacier Express exibe vistas desobstru\\u00eddas de paisagens \\u00fanicas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/suica_trem\\/suica_trem4.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"510\\\" height=\\\"340\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2><em><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Novidade: Excellence Class<br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/em>Luxo ainda maior em sua viagem de trem pelos Alpes Su\\u00ed\\u00e7os. Lugar na janela garantido, bar exclusivo, entretenimento a bordo, servi\\u00e7o de concierge e acompanhamento personalizado: a Excellence Class do Glacier Express eleva o luxo a um n\\u00edvel superior. A viagem entre St. Moritz e Zermatt envolve todos os sentidos: enquanto a paisagem espetacular desliza pela janela, o servi\\u00e7o de bordo come\\u00e7a oferecendo champagne e petiscos delicados \\u2013 e, depois, \\u00e9 servido o menu degusta\\u00e7\\u00e3o com sequ\\u00eancia de cinco pratos, sempre com a devida harmoniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de vinhos. A nova classe do Glacier Express traz um novo destaque de turismo de luxo na Su\\u00ed\\u00e7a.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/suica_trem\\/suica_trem5.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"582\\\" height=\\\"388\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/><\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2><br \\/><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Fatos Glacier Express<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>Rota: Zermatt \\u2013 St. Moritz ou vice-versa<br \\/>Dist\\u00e2ncia: 291 km<br \\/>Dura\\u00e7\\u00e3o: 8 h 03 min<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Dicas de excurs\\u00e3o<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>Matterhorn glacier paradise \\u2013 a vis\\u00e3o perfeita das enormes montanhas francesas, italianas e su\\u00ed\\u00e7as em um ponto a quase 4.000 metros de altitude<br \\/>Gornergrat \\u2013 vista do Matterhorn e de mais 28 picos de 4.000 metros de altura, a partir de um ponto a 3.131 metros<br \\/>Desfiladeiro do Reno \\u2013 uma aventura no \\u201cGrand Canyon\\u201d da Su\\u00ed\\u00e7a, entre Ilanz e Reichenau, realizada a p\\u00e9, de bicicleta ou em um barco de rafting<br \\/>Lago Sils \\u2013 a 1.800 metros acima do n\\u00edvel do mar, tem o transporte de barco de passageiros de maior altitude da Europa<br \\/>Corvatsch \\u2013 a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de cume mais alta da regi\\u00e3o leste dos Alpes, com 3.303 metros de altitude. Um para\\u00edso para esquiadores e f\\u00e3s de trilhas<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Comida &amp; Bebida<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>Refei\\u00e7\\u00e3o servida no assento do passageiro<br \\/>Menu do dia CHF 32 ou menu de 3 op\\u00e7\\u00f5es CHF 45 (02.03. \\u2013 13.10.2019)<br \\/>Refei\\u00e7\\u00f5es est\\u00e3o dispon\\u00edveis nos trens panor\\u00e2micos e podem ser requisitadas juntamente com a reserva do assento<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Luzern\\u2013Interlaken Express<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Lucerna e Interlaken \\u2013 dois dos destinos tur\\u00edsticos mais apreciados na Su\\u00ed\\u00e7a. Mas qual \\u00e9 a melhor maneira de ir de uma cidade para a outra? <br \\/>Muito f\\u00e1cil: tomando o Luzern\\u2013Interlaken Express e desfrutando da sua comodidade. O Luzern\\u2013Interlaken Express faz com que a viagem de uma cidade para a outra seja uma verdadeira experi\\u00eancia. Durante a viagem de aproximadamente duas horas \\u00e9 poss\\u00edvel admirar cinco lagos de montanha cristalinos, que acumulam a \\u00e1gua de diversos rios e cascatas. \\u00c0 margem do lago, escarpas \\u00edngremes de montanhas circundantes erguem-se protetoras criando, com isso, paisagens extraordin\\u00e1rias para fotografias.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/suica_trem\\/suica_trem6.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pouco antes de serpentear pelas alturas da passagem de Br\\u00fcnig, o trem comuta para o acionamento de cremalheira para poder vencer a subida. <br \\/>N\\u00e3o \\u00e9 \\u00e0 toa que o Luzern\\u2013Interlaken Express faz parte da GoldenPass Line, repleta de vistas panor\\u00e2micas, e que ainda leva de Interlaken para Montreux. Os passageiros que gostam de se informar t\\u00eam \\u00e0 sua disposi\\u00e7\\u00e3o o \\u201cLiveGuide\\u201d, app gratuito da Zentralbahn, companhia ferrovi\\u00e1ria.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Gra\\u00e7as \\u00e0 visualiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o do mapa, \\u00e9 poss\\u00edvel acompanhar ao vivo onde o trem se encontra no momento, e o pr\\u00f3ximo destaque ou informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es importantes da regi\\u00e3o s\\u00e3o notificados pontualmente via mensagens tipo \\u201cpush\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/suica_trem\\/suica_trem7.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Fatos<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>Etapa: Luzern \\u2013 Interlaken ou vice-versa<br \\/>Dist\\u00e2ncia: 98 km<br \\/>Dura\\u00e7\\u00e3o da viagem: 1 h 50 min<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Dicas de passeios<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>Lucerna e arredores<br \\/>Rigi (1.797 metros acima do mar)<br \\/>Stanserhorn (1.851 metros acima do mar)<br \\/>Interlaken e arredores<br \\/>Schilthorn (2.970 metros acima do mar)<br \\/>Museu ao ar livre de Ballenberg<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong>Comes e Bebes<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>Bistr\\u00f4 a partir de Luzern<br \\/>07:06 \\u2013 17:06 h, de maio at\\u00e9 outubro; 08:06 \\u2013 15:06 h de novembro at\\u00e9 abril<br \\/>Bistr\\u00f4 a partir de Interlaken<br \\/>09:04 \\u2013 19:04 h de maio at\\u00e9 outubro; 10:04 \\u2013 17:04 h de novembro at\\u00e9 abril<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><strong>Tabela de hor\\u00e1rios<\\/strong><\\/em><br \\/>Interlaken Ost \\u2013 Luzern<br \\/>Hor\\u00e1rio de 07:04 at\\u00e9 20:04 h<br \\/>Luzern \\u2013 Interlaken Ost<br \\/>Hor\\u00e1rio de 06:06 at\\u00e9 21:06 h<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fonte: Blog do Guru<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"10\",\"created\":\"2019-06-21 23:51:55\",\"created_by\":\"879\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-16 19:54:28\",\"modified_by\":\"879\",\"checked_out\":\"879\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-08-16 19:54:03\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-06-21 23:51:55\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog\\\\\\/suica_trem\\\\\\/suica_trem.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"right\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":7,\"ordering\":\"2\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"725\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(27, 4, 1, '', '2019-08-16 19:54:58', 879, 4730, '932f48dfd668cc026c35321aa19233a7a063bc65', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":\"82\",\"title\":\"Hot\\u00e9is de Bal Harbour oferecem privil\\u00e9gios exclusivos\",\"alias\":\"hoteis-de-bal-harbour-oferecem-privilegios-exclusivos\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Bal Harbour \\u00e9 hoje um dos destinos mais badalados de Miami e engloba o famoso Shopping ao ar livre, Bal Harbour Shops, com 100 das mais famosas grifes do mundo; o exclusivo cinco estrelas, de frente para o mar The Ritz-Carlton Bal Harbour, o hist\\u00f3rico e tradicional Sea View Hotel, o novo boutique hotel Bal Harbour Quarzo Hotel e o St. Regis Bal Harbour Resort. A cidade tamb\\u00e9m promove sess\\u00f5es de cinema ao ar livre e exposi\\u00e7\\u00f5es de arte p\\u00fablica pelas ruas da cidade. O destino oferece um programa gratuito que facilita a entrada de h\\u00f3spedes de Bal Harbour aos melhores museus de Miami.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Munidos de um cart\\u00e3o pessoal, eles t\\u00eam acesso gratuito a alguns dos mais aclamados museus e galerias privativas da regi\\u00e3o, como o Wolfsonian Museum; o Perez Art Museum (PAMM); o Museum of Contemporary Art (MOCA), a Rubell Family Collection; e a De La Cruz Collection.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\/hoteis_bal_harbour_st_regis.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"St. Regis\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" title=\\\"St. Regis\\\" caption=\\\"false\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"1024\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Os privil\\u00e9gios especiais s\\u00e3o v\\u00e1lidos para quem ficar hospedado em um dos 4 hot\\u00e9is de Bal Harbour \\u2013 St. Regis Bal Harbour, Ritz-Carlton Bal Harbour, Quarzo Bal Harbour e Sea View Hotel. A Flot Viagens montou um roteiro exclusivo com estes hot\\u00e9is, confira.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Confira a lista completa de museus que participam da a\\u00e7\\u00e3o:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Museum of Contemporary Art (MoCA)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>P\\u00e9rez Art Museum Miami (PAMM)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Phillip and Patricia Frost Museum of Science<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Fairchild Tropical Botanic Garden<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The Bass Museum of Art<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Wolfsonian \\u2013 FIU<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Patricia and Phillip frost Art Museum<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Rubell Family Collection (RFC)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The Margulies Collection at The Warehouse<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The de la Cruz Collection<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Institute of Contemporary Art (ICA)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>MDC Museum of Art and Design<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>National YoungArts Foundation<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>NSU Art Museum Fort Lauderdale<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>HistoryMiami Museum<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Jewish Museum of Florida \\u2013 FIU<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Lowe Art Museum \\u2013 University of Miami<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\/hoteis_bal_harbour_art_museum.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"P\\u00e9rez Art Museum Miami (PAMM)\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/blog\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\/hoteis_bal_harbour_museum_contemporany.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Museum of Contemporary Art (MoCA)\\\" title=\\\"Museum of Contemporary Art (MoCA)\\\" caption=\\\"false\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"495\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fonte: Blog do Guru<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"10\",\"created\":\"2019-06-21 23:51:55\",\"created_by\":\"879\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-16 19:54:58\",\"modified_by\":\"879\",\"checked_out\":\"879\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-08-16 19:54:33\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-06-21 23:51:55\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog\\\\\\/hoteis_bal_harbour\\\\\\/hoteis_bal_harbour.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"left\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":6,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0);
