(36, 7, 1, '', '2020-03-16 22:37:14', 879, 3690, 'f5a0178494cdb9c2b4f10fa5e37e3e6a7c214163', '{\"id\":7,\"asset_id\":\"87\",\"title\":\"Pacotes\",\"alias\":\"pacotes-tirado-do-submarino-viagens\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Na GD Turismo voc\\u00ea monta o pacote de viagem perfeito para voc\\u00ea e paga em at\\u00e9 10x sem juros. Aqui voc\\u00ea encontra pacotes de viagens baratos economiza at\\u00e9 30% na hora de montar o seu pacote tur\\u00edstico escolhendo a passagem a\\u00e9rea e o hotel em conjunto. A GD Turismo possui parceria com mais de 750 companhias a\\u00e9reas e mais de 250 mil hot\\u00e9is, por isso oferecemos os pre\\u00e7os mais baixos do mercado e ofertas exclusivas. Na GD Turismo voc\\u00ea encontra os melhores pre\\u00e7os de passagens a\\u00e9reas, hot\\u00e9is, cruzeiros e aluguel de carros para montar a sua viagem do seu jeito!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Entre os destinos nacionais, os pacotes que mais fazem sucesso s\\u00e3o para o Rio de Janeiro, Florian\\u00f3polis, Porto Seguro, Macei\\u00f3, Foz do Igua\\u00e7u, Bonito, S\\u00e3o Paulo, Fortaleza, Serra Ga\\u00facha e Curitiba. O Brasil tem destinos incr\\u00edveis que merecem ser explorados, ent\\u00e3o prepare a lista e comece a planejar sua viagem. Mas se o objetivo \\u00e9 viajar o mundo, voc\\u00ea tamb\\u00e9m encontra pacotes de viagens internacionais em lugares incr\\u00edveis como Buenos Aires, Mendoza, Montevid\\u00e9u, Santiago, Deserto do Atacama, Cartagena, Canc\\u00fan e Machu Picchu. Nos Estados Unidos, conhe\\u00e7a Nova York, S\\u00e3o Francisco, Orlando, Miami, Las Vegas e Los Angeles. J\\u00e1 na Europa, apaixone-se por Roma, Veneza, Londres, Munique, Berlim, Paris e Barcelona. Descubra tamb\\u00e9m as belezas do Leste Europeu na Rep\\u00fablica Tcheca e na Cro\\u00e1cia. Jap\\u00e3o, China e Tail\\u00e2ndia guardam destinos ex\\u00f3ticos incr\\u00edveis. Se a sua inten\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9 viajar com o crush, voc\\u00ea vai encontrar o pacote de viagem para casal perfeito pra voc\\u00eas! Al\\u00e9m disso, tem para fam\\u00edlia, galera, viagens sozinho e muito mais. Ent\\u00e3o n\\u00e3o perca mais tempo e garanta agora seu pacote!<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2020-02-21 21:32:30\",\"created_by\":\"879\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-03-16 22:37:14\",\"modified_by\":\"879\",\"checked_out\":\"879\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2020-03-16 22:37:03\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-02-21 21:32:30\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_b